verse.__text:
So God created man in his own image,


in the image of God he created him;


male and female he created them.

he said,







Cursed be Canaan;


a servant of servants shall he be to his brothers.

He called it Shibah;
 therefore the name of the city is 
Beersheba to this day.

Joseph answered Pharaoh, 
It is not in me; 
God will give Pharaoh a favorable answer.

Then Joseph said to Pharaoh, 
The dreams of Pharaoh are one; 
God has revealed to Pharaoh what he is about to do.

On the third day Joseph said to them, 
Do this and you will live, 
for I fear God:

And they said, 
You have saved our lives; 
may it please my lord, we will be servants to Pharaoh.

Simeon and Levi are brothers;


weapons 
of violence are their swords.

Judah, 
your brothers shall praise you;


your hand shall be on the neck of your enemies;


your father's sons shall bow down before you.

The 
scepter shall not depart from Judah,


nor the ruler's staff 
from between his feet,


until tribute comes to him;


and to him shall be the obedience of the peoples.

So do not fear; 
I will provide for you and your little ones.
 Thus he comforted them and spoke kindly to them.
